On March 9,2023 I endured 4 hours and 20 minutes to get my first tattoo as I waited almost 12 years actually to execute on getting it. The story of my @spartan race career has broken me; not an a way in which you may think. But in a memorable way of how much I’ve used up my body dedicating to the sport of OCR. The spear head is chipped and the handle is broken to represent how much it has been used in many competitive battles. A displayed reminder that the warrior spirit within me is not done using it; no matter how broken it maybe. In the end…we all know who already has the victory. 🙏🏻 I want to thank @plushgallerytattoo for being the perfect artist and friend who has known my story from the very beginning. Time to make some noise in the @crossfit arena. 
#ELESPARTANO
📸 @fosterphotomx

El 9 de marzo de 2023, soporté 4 horas y 20 minutos para hacerme mi primer tatuaje mientras esperaba casi 12 años para hacerlo. La historia de mi carrera en @spartan race me ha roto; no es una manera en la que puedes pensar. Pero de una forma memorable de lo mucho que he gastado mi cuerpo dedicándome al deporte del OCR. La punta de la lanza está astillada y el mango está roto para representar cuánto se ha utilizado en muchas batallas competitivas. Un recordatorio mostrado de que el espíritu guerrero dentro de mí no ha terminado de usarlo; no importa lo roto que esté. Al final… todos sabemos quién ya tiene la victoria. 🙏🏻 Quiero agradecer a @plushgallerytattoo por ser el artista y amigo perfecto que conoce mi historia desde el principio. Es hora de hacer algo de ruido en la arena de @crossfit.
#ELESPARTANO

As I reflect on competing at my very first individual CrossFit Games semifinals. All I can think of….. is the blessed ability to be able to compete. I faced a lot of new demons and overcame them through each and every event and I left knowing that this journey is just the beginning. I’m blessed for the love I had going into the weekend and I literally couldn’t have done it with out her by my side. ☀️ I learned, but most importantly matured alot with each and every event and I know moving forward that I’m wiser then I was before and have the right team beside me. G2G always 🙏 
#vamospormas

Reflexionando sobre el fin de semana pasado compitiendo en el semifinales individuales de los CrossFit Games. Todo en lo que puedo pensar... es en la bendita habilidad de poder competir a este nivel. Me enfrenté a muchos demonios nuevos que superé en todos y cada uno de los eventos y me fui sabiendo que este viaje es realmente solo el comienzo. Estoy bendecido por el amor que tuve durante el fin de semana y literalmente no podría haberlo hecho sin ella a mi lado ☀️ Aprendí, pero lo más importante, maduré mucho con todos y cada uno de los eventos y sé que tengo que seguir adelante. Soy más sabio que antes y tengo el equipo adecuado a mi lado. 💪 
#vamospormas

“Don’t let bitter, unhappy people drag you down to their level.
Instead, use their behaviour as an example of how not to behave and be grateful you are nothing like them.
Life is too big and time is too short to get caught up in there empty dreams.”

If your going through it, keep going through it. The battle wouldn’t have been presented to you to begin with, if you weren’t capable to overcome the task.
